title: Group Therapy: How Long to Heal After a Relationship
description: Maya wants to know if it's necessary to take time to heal after a relationship versus jumping into another relationship.  She has taken time to heal before but now she's out of another relationship and doesn't feel like she really needs to even though she was cheated on.
